WEBVTT

30:33.855 --> 30:36.772
There's this girl in jazz band, Piper.

30:37.230 --> 30:38.355
She started to ditch with me.

30:38.730 --> 30:39.480
But then Kevin...

30:39.772 --> 30:40.397
Who's Kevin?

30:41.063 --> 30:41.772
My best friend.

30:42.480 --> 30:43.147
At least he was.

30:43.480 --> 30:44.147
What'd Kevin do?

30:44.563 --> 30:46.063
Kevin found out I wanted to ditch too.

30:46.355 --> 30:47.688
But he's not even in jazz band.

30:47.980 --> 30:49.105
He just wanted to hang out with Piper.

30:49.647 --> 30:50.897
I was the one hanging out with Piper.

30:51.397 --> 30:52.980
So I'm supposed to go in and change his

30:52.980 --> 30:54.772
absence in a present
so he can hang out with Piper?

30:55.480 --> 30:55.855
Bullshit.

30:56.272 --> 30:58.147
So instead, I gave
him three more absints.

30:58.730 --> 30:58.980
Good.

30:59.522 --> 31:00.063
Send a message.

31:00.313 --> 31:01.980
He got busted and
told the vice principal.

31:03.022 --> 31:03.188
Kevin.
